(715, 1, '2021-11-02 17:10:43', '2021-11-02 16:10:43', '<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":377,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/shema-groupe-cours/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":27} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:27% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/shema-groupe-cours-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-377 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"vivid-red\",\"fontSize\":\"huge\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-huge-font-size\">Les notions générales :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>1-</strong> Phase d\'élaboration d\'un programme :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Un programme avant son introduction en production (opérationnelle) se passe en <strong>4 phases </strong>: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Phase d\'<strong>analyse</strong></li><li>Phase de <strong>spécialisation</strong></li><li>Phase de <strong>traduction</strong></li><li>Phase d\'<strong>exécution</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br><strong>2-</strong> Phase d’analyse :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A partir du cahier des charges ( besoin du client) du problème posé en informatique, le concepteur de la solutions doit élaborer un <strong>modèle conceptuel d’analyse</strong> (MCA) qui décrit la solution sous la forme d’une suite d’étapes et d’actions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Deux méthodes sont formaliser dans la création du MCA&nbsp;: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":387,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/capture-6/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-387 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>2.1. </strong>La méthode <strong>ascendante&nbsp;</strong>: le concepteur compose la solution informatique du problème à partir d’une <strong>boîte à outils&nbsp; algorithme</strong> élémentaire (connu et maîtrisé). Il obtient&nbsp;un arbres sur divisé en niveaux de difficulté ascendante&nbsp;chaque étape est composée d’action simples.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":390,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/capture-7/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-9.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-390 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Contenu…\"} -->\n<p><strong>2.2.</strong> &nbsp;La méthode <strong>descente&nbsp;</strong>: le concepteur&nbsp;<strong>subdivise </strong>le problème posé en plusieurs sous problèmes. Si ces derniers&nbsp;n’ont pas de <strong>solutions simples ou connues</strong>, ils seront de nouveau subdivisés. on obtient alors un arbres subdiviser au niveau de difficulté descendant.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exemple 1&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Elaborer un MCA qui permet la préparation d’une omelette :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":385,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-385\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exemple 2&nbsp;: Elaborer un MCA qui calcul la moyenne de trois notes&nbsp;:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":386,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-7.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-386\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exercice :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Elaborer un MCA qui permet de calculer la surface et le périmètre d’un rectangle:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":381,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-381\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Elaborer un MCA qui permet de&nbsp; saisir un temps exprimer en heure, min, sec et afficher son équivalent en seconde.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":382,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-382\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>MCA algorithme</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n\n<p class=\"para-cours\">\nSaisir: <br>\nn1, n2, n3 <br> <br>\nOpération: <br>\nSomme = n1 + n2 + n3 <br>\nMoyenne = Somme / 3  <br><br>\nAfficher: <br>\nMoyenne\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Langage : C</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>float </em>n;\n    <em>float </em>note;\n    <em>float </em>somme = 0, moy;\n    printf(\"Combien de note voulez-vous saisir ?\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;n);\n\n    <em>for </em>(<em>int </em>i = 0; i &lt; n; i++){\n        printf(\"Saisir note \\n>>\");\n        scanf(\"%f\", &amp;note);\n        somme += note;\n    }\n\n    moy = somme / n;\n\n    printf(\"Moyenne note = %.2f\", moy);\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Langage : PHP</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form action=\"moyenne.php\" method=\"post\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n1\" placeholder=\"Note 1\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n2\" placeholder=\"Note 2\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n3\" placeholder=\"Note 3\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"submit\" name=\"btn\" value=\"OK\"&gt;\n&lt;/form&gt;</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;?php\n$_note1 = $_POST[\'n1\'];\n$_note2 = $_POST[\'n2\'];\n$_note3 = $_POST[\'n3\'];\n$somme = $_note1 + $_note2 + $_note3;\n$moy = round($somme / 3, 2);\necho \"&lt;p&gt;Moyenne : $moy&lt;/p&gt;\";\n?&gt;</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\">Calcul surface &amp; périmètre</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\"> Calcul surface &amp; périmètre </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\"> Calcul surface &amp; périmètre </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>declaration : L, l, peri, surface = réel</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"saisir longueur\")</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (L)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"saisir largeur\")</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (l)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>peri &lt;- 2 * L + 2 * l</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>surface &lt;- L * l</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"surface: \", surface)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"perimètre: \", péri)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin calcul_surface_perimetre</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n</strong>\n<strong><em>int </em>main() {\n    <em>float </em>L, l, peri, surface;\n\n    printf(\"Saisir la longueur \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;L);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir la largeur \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;l);\n\n    peri = 2 * L + 2 * l;\n    surface = L * l;\n\n    printf(\"Perim%ctre = %f\\n\", 130, peri);\n    printf(\"Surface = %f\", surface);\n    <em>return </em>0;\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"rectangle.php\" <em>method</em>=\"POST\">\n\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"text\" <em>name</em>=\"longueur\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Longueur\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"text\" <em>name</em>=\"Largeur\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Largeur\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"reset\" <em>value</em>=\"Annuler\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'longueur\']) &amp;&amp; !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'Largeur\'])) {\n            $longueur = $_POST[\'longueur\'];\n            $largeur = $_POST[\'Largeur\'];\n\n            $sur = $longueur * $largeur;\n            $peri = 2 * ($longueur * $largeur);\n\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>surface : $sur\";\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;br>\";\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Périmètre : $peri&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else</em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>il manque quelque chose&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n\n    }\n\n\n    <em>?>\n\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Calculer l\'aire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Calculer l\'aire  </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Calculer l\'aire  </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Déclaration : RT, RL, TL, R = réel</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir RT”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (RT)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir RL”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (RL)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir TL”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (TL)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir R”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (R)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A1 &lt;- TL * RT * 2</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A2 &lt;- (R - RL) * TL</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A &lt;- A1 - A2</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher(A)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin Aire</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>float </em>RT, RL, TL, R;\n\n    printf(\"Saisir RT\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;RT);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir RL\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;RL);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir TL\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;TL);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir R\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;R);\n\n    <em>float </em>A1 = TL * RT * 2;\n    <em>float </em>A2 = (R - RL) * TL;\n    <em>float </em>A = A1 - A2;\n\n    printf(\"Aire: %.2f\", A);\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"Aire.php\" <em>method</em>=\"post\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"RT\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"RT\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"RL\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"RL\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"TL\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"TL\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"Rayon\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Rayon\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'RT\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'RL\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'TL\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'Rayon\'])) {\n\n            $RT = $_POST[\'RT\'];\n            $RL = $_POST[\'RL\'];\n            $TL = $_POST[\'TL\'];\n            $Rayon = $_POST[\'Rayon\'];\n\n            $A1 = $TL * $RT * 2;\n            $A2 = ($Rayon - $RL) * $TL;\n            $Aire = $A1 + $A2;\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Aire : $Aire&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else </em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Renseigner tous les champs&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n    }\n    <em>?>\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Salaire</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Salaire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Salaire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>déclaration</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>heure, jour: entier</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>benef, P, R : entier</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir heure”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (heure)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir jour”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (jour)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir benef”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (benef)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“Pourcentage”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (P)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“R”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (R)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>SB &lt;- R * jour * heure</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Prime &lt;- P * benef / 100</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Salaire &lt;- SB + Prime</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher(Salaire)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin Calcul_Salaire</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>int </em>heure, jour, benef, P, R, SB, Prime, Salaire;\n\n    printf(\"Heure\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;heure);\n\n    printf(\"Jour\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;jour);\n\n    printf(\"benef\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;benef);\n\n    printf(\"pourcentage\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;P);\n\n    printf(\"r%cmun%cration\\n>>\", 130, 130);\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;R);\n\n    SB = R * jour * heure;\n    Prime = P * benef / 100;\n    Salaire = SB + Prime;\n\n    printf(\"Salaire : %d\", Salaire);\n\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"salaire.php\" <em>method</em>=\"post\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"heure\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Heure\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"jour\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Jour\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"benef\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Benef\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"pourcentage\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Pourcentage\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"remu\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Rémunération\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'heure\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'jour\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'benef\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'pourcentage\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'remu\'])) {\n\n            $heure = $_POST[\'heure\'];\n            $jour = $_POST[\'jour\'];\n            $benef = $_POST[\'benef\'];\n            $pour = $_POST[\'pourcentage\'];\n            $remu = $_POST[\'remu\'];\n\n\n            $SB = $remu * $jour * $heure;\n            $Prime = $pour * $benef / 100;\n            $salaire = $SB + $Prime;\n\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Salaire : $salaire&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else </em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Il manque un truc&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n    }\n    <em>?>\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'COURS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '243-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-11-02 17:10:43', '2021-11-02 16:10:43', '', 243, 'http://localhost/projetgroupe/?p=715', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(717, 1, '2021-11-02 17:11:20', '2021-11-02 16:11:20', '<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":377,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/shema-groupe-cours/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":27} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:27% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/shema-groupe-cours-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-377 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"vivid-red\",\"fontSize\":\"huge\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-huge-font-size\">Les notions générales :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>1-</strong> Phase d\'élaboration d\'un programme :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Un programme avant son introduction en production (opérationnelle) se passe en <strong>4 phases </strong>: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Phase d\'<strong>analyse</strong></li><li>Phase de <strong>spécialisation</strong></li><li>Phase de <strong>traduction</strong></li><li>Phase d\'<strong>exécution</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br><strong>2-</strong> Phase d’analyse :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A partir du cahier des charges ( besoin du client) du problème posé en informatique, le concepteur de la solutions doit élaborer un <strong>modèle conceptuel d’analyse</strong> (MCA) qui décrit la solution sous la forme d’une suite d’étapes et d’actions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Deux méthodes sont formaliser dans la création du MCA&nbsp;: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":387,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/capture-6/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-387 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>2.1. </strong>La méthode <strong>ascendante&nbsp;</strong>: le concepteur compose la solution informatique du problème à partir d’une <strong>boîte à outils&nbsp; algorithme</strong> élémentaire (connu et maîtrisé). Il obtient&nbsp;un arbres sur divisé en niveaux de difficulté ascendante&nbsp;chaque étape est composée d’action simples.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":390,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/capture-7/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-9.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-390 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Contenu…\"} -->\n<p><strong>2.2.</strong> &nbsp;La méthode <strong>descente&nbsp;</strong>: le concepteur&nbsp;<strong>subdivise </strong>le problème posé en plusieurs sous problèmes. Si ces derniers&nbsp;n’ont pas de <strong>solutions simples ou connues</strong>, ils seront de nouveau subdivisés. on obtient alors un arbres subdiviser au niveau de difficulté descendant.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exemple 1&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Elaborer un MCA qui permet la préparation d’une omelette :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":385,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-385\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exemple 2&nbsp;: Elaborer un MCA qui calcul la moyenne de trois notes&nbsp;:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":386,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-7.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-386\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exercice :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Elaborer un MCA qui permet de calculer la surface et le périmètre d’un rectangle:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":381,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-381\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Elaborer un MCA qui permet de&nbsp; saisir un temps exprimer en heure, min, sec et afficher son équivalent en seconde.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":382,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-382\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>MCA algorithme</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n\n<p class=\"para-cours\">\nSaisir: <br>\nn1, n2, n3 <br> <br>\nOpération: <br>\nSomme = n1 + n2 + n3 <br>\nMoyenne = Somme / 3  <br><br>\nAfficher: <br>\nMoyenne\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Langage : C</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>float </em>n;\n    <em>float </em>note;\n    <em>float </em>somme = 0, moy;\n    printf(\"Combien de note voulez-vous saisir ?\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;n);\n\n    <em>for </em>(<em>int </em>i = 0; i &lt; n; i++){\n        printf(\"Saisir note \\n>>\");\n        scanf(\"%f\", &amp;note);\n        somme += note;\n    }\n\n    moy = somme / n;\n\n    printf(\"Moyenne note = %.2f\", moy);\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Langage : PHP</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form action=\"moyenne.php\" method=\"post\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n1\" placeholder=\"Note 1\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n2\" placeholder=\"Note 2\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n3\" placeholder=\"Note 3\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"submit\" name=\"btn\" value=\"OK\"&gt;\n&lt;/form&gt;</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;?php\n$_note1 = $_POST[\'n1\'];\n$_note2 = $_POST[\'n2\'];\n$_note3 = $_POST[\'n3\'];\n$somme = $_note1 + $_note2 + $_note3;\n$moy = round($somme / 3, 2);\necho \"&lt;p&gt;Moyenne : $moy&lt;/p&gt;\";\n?&gt;</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\">Calcul surface &amp; périmètre</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\"> Calcul surface &amp; périmètre </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\"> Calcul surface &amp; périmètre </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>declaration : L, l, peri, surface = réel</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"saisir longueur\")</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (L)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"saisir largeur\")</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (l)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>peri &lt;- 2 * L + 2 * l</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>surface &lt;- L * l</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"surface: \", surface)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"perimètre: \", péri)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin calcul_surface_perimetre</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n</strong>\n<strong><em>int </em>main() {\n    <em>float </em>L, l, peri, surface;\n\n    printf(\"Saisir la longueur \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;L);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir la largeur \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;l);\n\n    peri = 2 * L + 2 * l;\n    surface = L * l;\n\n    printf(\"Perim%ctre = %f\\n\", 130, peri);\n    printf(\"Surface = %f\", surface);\n    <em>return </em>0;\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"rectangle.php\" <em>method</em>=\"POST\">\n\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"text\" <em>name</em>=\"longueur\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Longueur\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"text\" <em>name</em>=\"Largeur\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Largeur\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"reset\" <em>value</em>=\"Annuler\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'longueur\']) &amp;&amp; !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'Largeur\'])) {\n            $longueur = $_POST[\'longueur\'];\n            $largeur = $_POST[\'Largeur\'];\n\n            $sur = $longueur * $largeur;\n            $peri = 2 * ($longueur * $largeur);\n\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>surface : $sur\";\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;br>\";\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Périmètre : $peri&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else</em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>il manque quelque chose&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n\n    }\n\n\n    <em>?>\n\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Calculer l\'aire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Calculer l\'aire  </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Calculer l\'aire  </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Déclaration : RT, RL, TL, R = réel</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir RT”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (RT)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir RL”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (RL)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir TL”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (TL)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir R”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (R)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A1 &lt;- TL * RT * 2</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A2 &lt;- (R - RL) * TL</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A &lt;- A1 - A2</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher(A)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin Aire</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>float </em>RT, RL, TL, R;\n\n    printf(\"Saisir RT\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;RT);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir RL\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;RL);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir TL\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;TL);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir R\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;R);\n\n    <em>float </em>A1 = TL * RT * 2;\n    <em>float </em>A2 = (R - RL) * TL;\n    <em>float </em>A = A1 - A2;\n\n    printf(\"Aire: %.2f\", A);\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"Aire.php\" <em>method</em>=\"post\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"RT\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"RT\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"RL\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"RL\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"TL\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"TL\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"Rayon\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Rayon\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'RT\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'RL\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'TL\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'Rayon\'])) {\n\n            $RT = $_POST[\'RT\'];\n            $RL = $_POST[\'RL\'];\n            $TL = $_POST[\'TL\'];\n            $Rayon = $_POST[\'Rayon\'];\n\n            $A1 = $TL * $RT * 2;\n            $A2 = ($Rayon - $RL) * $TL;\n            $Aire = $A1 + $A2;\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Aire : $Aire&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else </em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Renseigner tous les champs&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n    }\n    <em>?>\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Salaire</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Salaire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Salaire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>déclaration</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>heure, jour: entier</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>benef, P, R : entier</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir heure”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (heure)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir jour”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (jour)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir benef”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (benef)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“Pourcentage”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (P)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“R”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (R)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>SB &lt;- R * jour * heure</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Prime &lt;- P * benef / 100</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Salaire &lt;- SB + Prime</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher(Salaire)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin Calcul_Salaire</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>int </em>heure, jour, benef, P, R, SB, Prime, Salaire;\n\n    printf(\"Heure\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;heure);\n\n    printf(\"Jour\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;jour);\n\n    printf(\"benef\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;benef);\n\n    printf(\"pourcentage\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;P);\n\n    printf(\"r%cmun%cration\\n>>\", 130, 130);\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;R);\n\n    SB = R * jour * heure;\n    Prime = P * benef / 100;\n    Salaire = SB + Prime;\n\n    printf(\"Salaire : %d\", Salaire);\n\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"salaire.php\" <em>method</em>=\"post\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"heure\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Heure\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"jour\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Jour\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"benef\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Benef\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"pourcentage\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Pourcentage\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"remu\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Rémunération\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'heure\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'jour\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'benef\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'pourcentage\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'remu\'])) {\n\n            $heure = $_POST[\'heure\'];\n            $jour = $_POST[\'jour\'];\n            $benef = $_POST[\'benef\'];\n            $pour = $_POST[\'pourcentage\'];\n            $remu = $_POST[\'remu\'];\n\n\n            $SB = $remu * $jour * $heure;\n            $Prime = $pour * $benef / 100;\n            $salaire = $SB + $Prime;\n\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Salaire : $salaire&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else </em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Il manque un truc&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n    }\n    <em>?>\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'COURS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '243-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-11-02 17:11:20', '2021-11-02 16:11:20', '', 243, 'http://localhost/projetgroupe/?p=717', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(719, 1, '2021-11-02 17:13:12', '2021-11-02 16:13:12', '<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":377,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/shema-groupe-cours/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":27} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:27% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/shema-groupe-cours-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-377 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"vivid-red\",\"fontSize\":\"huge\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-huge-font-size\">Les notions générales :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>1-</strong> Phase d\'élaboration d\'un programme :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Un programme avant son introduction en production (opérationnelle) se passe en <strong>4 phases </strong>: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Phase d\'<strong>analyse</strong></li><li>Phase de <strong>spécialisation</strong></li><li>Phase de <strong>traduction</strong></li><li>Phase d\'<strong>exécution</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br><strong>2-</strong> Phase d’analyse :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A partir du cahier des charges ( besoin du client) du problème posé en informatique, le concepteur de la solutions doit élaborer un <strong>modèle conceptuel d’analyse</strong> (MCA) qui décrit la solution sous la forme d’une suite d’étapes et d’actions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Deux méthodes sont formaliser dans la création du MCA&nbsp;: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":387,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/capture-6/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-387 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>2.1. </strong>La méthode <strong>ascendante&nbsp;</strong>: le concepteur compose la solution informatique du problème à partir d’une <strong>boîte à outils&nbsp; algorithme</strong> élémentaire (connu et maîtrisé). Il obtient&nbsp;un arbres sur divisé en niveaux de difficulté ascendante&nbsp;chaque étape est composée d’action simples.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":390,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/capture-7/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-9.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-390 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Contenu…\"} -->\n<p><strong>2.2.</strong> &nbsp;La méthode <strong>descente&nbsp;</strong>: le concepteur&nbsp;<strong>subdivise </strong>le problème posé en plusieurs sous problèmes. Si ces derniers&nbsp;n’ont pas de <strong>solutions simples ou connues</strong>, ils seront de nouveau subdivisés. on obtient alors un arbres subdiviser au niveau de difficulté descendant.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exemple 1&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Elaborer un MCA qui permet la préparation d’une omelette :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":385,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-385\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exemple 2&nbsp;: Elaborer un MCA qui calcul la moyenne de trois notes&nbsp;:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":386,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-7.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-386\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exercice :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Elaborer un MCA qui permet de calculer la surface et le périmètre d’un rectangle:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":381,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-381\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Elaborer un MCA qui permet de&nbsp; saisir un temps exprimer en heure, min, sec et afficher son équivalent en seconde.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":382,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-382\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>MCA algorithme</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n\n<p class=\"para-cours\">\nSaisir: <br>\nn1, n2, n3 <br> <br>\nOpération: <br>\nSomme = n1 + n2 + n3 <br>\nMoyenne = Somme / 3  <br><br>\nAfficher: <br>\nMoyenne\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Langage : C</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>float </em>n;\n    <em>float </em>note;\n    <em>float </em>somme = 0, moy;\n    printf(\"Combien de note voulez-vous saisir ?\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;n);\n\n    <em>for </em>(<em>int </em>i = 0; i &lt; n; i++){\n        printf(\"Saisir note \\n>>\");\n        scanf(\"%f\", &amp;note);\n        somme += note;\n    }\n\n    moy = somme / n;\n\n    printf(\"Moyenne note = %.2f\", moy);\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Langage : PHP</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form action=\"moyenne.php\" method=\"post\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n1\" placeholder=\"Note 1\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n2\" placeholder=\"Note 2\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n3\" placeholder=\"Note 3\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"submit\" name=\"btn\" value=\"OK\"&gt;\n&lt;/form&gt;</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;?php\n$_note1 = $_POST[\'n1\'];\n$_note2 = $_POST[\'n2\'];\n$_note3 = $_POST[\'n3\'];\n$somme = $_note1 + $_note2 + $_note3;\n$moy = round($somme / 3, 2);\necho \"&lt;p&gt;Moyenne : $moy&lt;/p&gt;\";\n?&gt;</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\">Calcul surface &amp; périmètre</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\"> Calcul surface &amp; périmètre </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\"> Calcul surface &amp; périmètre </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>declaration : L, l, peri, surface = réel</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"saisir longueur\")</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (L)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"saisir largeur\")</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (l)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>peri &lt;- 2 * L + 2 * l</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>surface &lt;- L * l</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"surface: \", surface)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"perimètre: \", péri)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin calcul_surface_perimetre</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n</strong>\n<strong><em>int </em>main() {\n    <em>float </em>L, l, peri, surface;\n\n    printf(\"Saisir la longueur \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;L);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir la largeur \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;l);\n\n    peri = 2 * L + 2 * l;\n    surface = L * l;\n\n    printf(\"Perim%ctre = %f\\n\", 130, peri);\n    printf(\"Surface = %f\", surface);\n    <em>return </em>0;\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"rectangle.php\" <em>method</em>=\"POST\">\n\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"text\" <em>name</em>=\"longueur\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Longueur\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"text\" <em>name</em>=\"Largeur\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Largeur\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"reset\" <em>value</em>=\"Annuler\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'longueur\']) &amp;&amp; !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'Largeur\'])) {\n            $longueur = $_POST[\'longueur\'];\n            $largeur = $_POST[\'Largeur\'];\n\n            $sur = $longueur * $largeur;\n            $peri = 2 * ($longueur * $largeur);\n\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>surface : $sur\";\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;br>\";\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Périmètre : $peri&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else</em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>il manque quelque chose&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n\n    }\n\n\n    <em>?>\n\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Calculer l\'aire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Calculer l\'aire  </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Calculer l\'aire  </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Déclaration : RT, RL, TL, R = réel</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir RT”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (RT)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir RL”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (RL)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir TL”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (TL)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir R”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (R)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A1 &lt;- TL * RT * 2</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A2 &lt;- (R - RL) * TL</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A &lt;- A1 - A2</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher(A)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin Aire</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>float </em>RT, RL, TL, R;\n\n    printf(\"Saisir RT\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;RT);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir RL\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;RL);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir TL\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;TL);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir R\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;R);\n\n    <em>float </em>A1 = TL * RT * 2;\n    <em>float </em>A2 = (R - RL) * TL;\n    <em>float </em>A = A1 - A2;\n\n    printf(\"Aire: %.2f\", A);\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"Aire.php\" <em>method</em>=\"post\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"RT\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"RT\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"RL\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"RL\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"TL\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"TL\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"Rayon\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Rayon\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'RT\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'RL\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'TL\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'Rayon\'])) {\n\n            $RT = $_POST[\'RT\'];\n            $RL = $_POST[\'RL\'];\n            $TL = $_POST[\'TL\'];\n            $Rayon = $_POST[\'Rayon\'];\n\n            $A1 = $TL * $RT * 2;\n            $A2 = ($Rayon - $RL) * $TL;\n            $Aire = $A1 + $A2;\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Aire : $Aire&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else </em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Renseigner tous les champs&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n    }\n    <em>?>\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Salaire</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Salaire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Salaire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>déclaration</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>heure, jour: entier</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>benef, P, R : entier</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir heure”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (heure)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir jour”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (jour)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir benef”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (benef)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“Pourcentage”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (P)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“R”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (R)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>SB &lt;- R * jour * heure</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Prime &lt;- P * benef / 100</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Salaire &lt;- SB + Prime</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher(Salaire)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin Calcul_Salaire</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>int </em>heure, jour, benef, P, R, SB, Prime, Salaire;\n\n    printf(\"Heure\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;heure);\n\n    printf(\"Jour\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;jour);\n\n    printf(\"benef\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;benef);\n\n    printf(\"pourcentage\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;P);\n\n    printf(\"r%cmun%cration\\n>>\", 130, 130);\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;R);\n\n    SB = R * jour * heure;\n    Prime = P * benef / 100;\n    Salaire = SB + Prime;\n\n    printf(\"Salaire : %d\", Salaire);\n\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"salaire.php\" <em>method</em>=\"post\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"heure\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Heure\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"jour\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Jour\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"benef\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Benef\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"pourcentage\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Pourcentage\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"remu\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Rémunération\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'heure\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'jour\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'benef\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'pourcentage\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'remu\'])) {\n\n            $heure = $_POST[\'heure\'];\n            $jour = $_POST[\'jour\'];\n            $benef = $_POST[\'benef\'];\n            $pour = $_POST[\'pourcentage\'];\n            $remu = $_POST[\'remu\'];\n\n\n            $SB = $remu * $jour * $heure;\n            $Prime = $pour * $benef / 100;\n            $salaire = $SB + $Prime;\n\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Salaire : $salaire&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else </em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Il manque un truc&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n    }\n    <em>?>\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Additionner deux heure résultat en seconde</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Additionner deux heure résultat en seconde </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Additionner deux heure résultat en seconde </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'COURS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '243-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-11-02 17:13:12', '2021-11-02 16:13:12', '', 243, 'http://localhost/projetgroupe/?p=719', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(722, 1, '2021-11-02 17:14:52', '2021-11-02 16:14:52', '<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":377,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/shema-groupe-cours/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":27} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:27% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/shema-groupe-cours-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-377 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"vivid-red\",\"fontSize\":\"huge\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-huge-font-size\">Les notions générales :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>1-</strong> Phase d\'élaboration d\'un programme :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Un programme avant son introduction en production (opérationnelle) se passe en <strong>4 phases </strong>: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Phase d\'<strong>analyse</strong></li><li>Phase de <strong>spécialisation</strong></li><li>Phase de <strong>traduction</strong></li><li>Phase d\'<strong>exécution</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br><strong>2-</strong> Phase d’analyse :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A partir du cahier des charges ( besoin du client) du problème posé en informatique, le concepteur de la solutions doit élaborer un <strong>modèle conceptuel d’analyse</strong> (MCA) qui décrit la solution sous la forme d’une suite d’étapes et d’actions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Deux méthodes sont formaliser dans la création du MCA&nbsp;: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":387,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/capture-6/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-387 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>2.1. </strong>La méthode <strong>ascendante&nbsp;</strong>: le concepteur compose la solution informatique du problème à partir d’une <strong>boîte à outils&nbsp; algorithme</strong> élémentaire (connu et maîtrisé). Il obtient&nbsp;un arbres sur divisé en niveaux de difficulté ascendante&nbsp;chaque étape est composée d’action simples.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":390,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/capture-7/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-9.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-390 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Contenu…\"} -->\n<p><strong>2.2.</strong> &nbsp;La méthode <strong>descente&nbsp;</strong>: le concepteur&nbsp;<strong>subdivise </strong>le problème posé en plusieurs sous problèmes. Si ces derniers&nbsp;n’ont pas de <strong>solutions simples ou connues</strong>, ils seront de nouveau subdivisés. on obtient alors un arbres subdiviser au niveau de difficulté descendant.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exemple 1&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Elaborer un MCA qui permet la préparation d’une omelette :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":385,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-385\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exemple 2&nbsp;: Elaborer un MCA qui calcul la moyenne de trois notes&nbsp;:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":386,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-7.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-386\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exercice :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Elaborer un MCA qui permet de calculer la surface et le périmètre d’un rectangle:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":381,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-381\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Elaborer un MCA qui permet de&nbsp; saisir un temps exprimer en heure, min, sec et afficher son équivalent en seconde.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":382,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-382\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>MCA algorithme</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n\n<p class=\"para-cours\">\nSaisir: <br>\nn1, n2, n3 <br> <br>\nOpération: <br>\nSomme = n1 + n2 + n3 <br>\nMoyenne = Somme / 3  <br><br>\nAfficher: <br>\nMoyenne\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Langage : C</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>float </em>n;\n    <em>float </em>note;\n    <em>float </em>somme = 0, moy;\n    printf(\"Combien de note voulez-vous saisir ?\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;n);\n\n    <em>for </em>(<em>int </em>i = 0; i &lt; n; i++){\n        printf(\"Saisir note \\n>>\");\n        scanf(\"%f\", &amp;note);\n        somme += note;\n    }\n\n    moy = somme / n;\n\n    printf(\"Moyenne note = %.2f\", moy);\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Langage : PHP</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form action=\"moyenne.php\" method=\"post\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n1\" placeholder=\"Note 1\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n2\" placeholder=\"Note 2\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n3\" placeholder=\"Note 3\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"submit\" name=\"btn\" value=\"OK\"&gt;\n&lt;/form&gt;</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;?php\n$_note1 = $_POST[\'n1\'];\n$_note2 = $_POST[\'n2\'];\n$_note3 = $_POST[\'n3\'];\n$somme = $_note1 + $_note2 + $_note3;\n$moy = round($somme / 3, 2);\necho \"&lt;p&gt;Moyenne : $moy&lt;/p&gt;\";\n?&gt;</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\">Calcul surface &amp; périmètre</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\"> Calcul surface &amp; périmètre </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\"> Calcul surface &amp; périmètre </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>declaration : L, l, peri, surface = réel</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"saisir longueur\")</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (L)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"saisir largeur\")</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (l)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>peri &lt;- 2 * L + 2 * l</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>surface &lt;- L * l</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"surface: \", surface)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"perimètre: \", péri)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin calcul_surface_perimetre</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n</strong>\n<strong><em>int </em>main() {\n    <em>float </em>L, l, peri, surface;\n\n    printf(\"Saisir la longueur \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;L);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir la largeur \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;l);\n\n    peri = 2 * L + 2 * l;\n    surface = L * l;\n\n    printf(\"Perim%ctre = %f\\n\", 130, peri);\n    printf(\"Surface = %f\", surface);\n    <em>return </em>0;\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"rectangle.php\" <em>method</em>=\"POST\">\n\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"text\" <em>name</em>=\"longueur\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Longueur\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"text\" <em>name</em>=\"Largeur\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Largeur\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"reset\" <em>value</em>=\"Annuler\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'longueur\']) &amp;&amp; !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'Largeur\'])) {\n            $longueur = $_POST[\'longueur\'];\n            $largeur = $_POST[\'Largeur\'];\n\n            $sur = $longueur * $largeur;\n            $peri = 2 * ($longueur * $largeur);\n\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>surface : $sur\";\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;br>\";\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Périmètre : $peri&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else</em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>il manque quelque chose&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n\n    }\n\n\n    <em>?>\n\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Calculer l\'aire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Calculer l\'aire  </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Calculer l\'aire  </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Déclaration : RT, RL, TL, R = réel</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir RT”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (RT)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir RL”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (RL)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir TL”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (TL)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir R”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (R)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A1 &lt;- TL * RT * 2</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A2 &lt;- (R - RL) * TL</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A &lt;- A1 - A2</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher(A)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin Aire</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>float </em>RT, RL, TL, R;\n\n    printf(\"Saisir RT\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;RT);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir RL\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;RL);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir TL\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;TL);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir R\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;R);\n\n    <em>float </em>A1 = TL * RT * 2;\n    <em>float </em>A2 = (R - RL) * TL;\n    <em>float </em>A = A1 - A2;\n\n    printf(\"Aire: %.2f\", A);\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"Aire.php\" <em>method</em>=\"post\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"RT\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"RT\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"RL\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"RL\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"TL\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"TL\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"Rayon\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Rayon\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'RT\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'RL\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'TL\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'Rayon\'])) {\n\n            $RT = $_POST[\'RT\'];\n            $RL = $_POST[\'RL\'];\n            $TL = $_POST[\'TL\'];\n            $Rayon = $_POST[\'Rayon\'];\n\n            $A1 = $TL * $RT * 2;\n            $A2 = ($Rayon - $RL) * $TL;\n            $Aire = $A1 + $A2;\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Aire : $Aire&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else </em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Renseigner tous les champs&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n    }\n    <em>?>\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Salaire</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Salaire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Salaire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>déclaration</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>heure, jour: entier</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>benef, P, R : entier</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir heure”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (heure)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir jour”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (jour)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir benef”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (benef)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“Pourcentage”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (P)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“R”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (R)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>SB &lt;- R * jour * heure</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Prime &lt;- P * benef / 100</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Salaire &lt;- SB + Prime</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher(Salaire)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin Calcul_Salaire</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>int </em>heure, jour, benef, P, R, SB, Prime, Salaire;\n\n    printf(\"Heure\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;heure);\n\n    printf(\"Jour\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;jour);\n\n    printf(\"benef\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;benef);\n\n    printf(\"pourcentage\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;P);\n\n    printf(\"r%cmun%cration\\n>>\", 130, 130);\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;R);\n\n    SB = R * jour * heure;\n    Prime = P * benef / 100;\n    Salaire = SB + Prime;\n\n    printf(\"Salaire : %d\", Salaire);\n\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"salaire.php\" <em>method</em>=\"post\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"heure\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Heure\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"jour\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Jour\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"benef\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Benef\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"pourcentage\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Pourcentage\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"remu\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Rémunération\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'heure\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'jour\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'benef\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'pourcentage\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'remu\'])) {\n\n            $heure = $_POST[\'heure\'];\n            $jour = $_POST[\'jour\'];\n            $benef = $_POST[\'benef\'];\n            $pour = $_POST[\'pourcentage\'];\n            $remu = $_POST[\'remu\'];\n\n\n            $SB = $remu * $jour * $heure;\n            $Prime = $pour * $benef / 100;\n            $salaire = $SB + $Prime;\n\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Salaire : $salaire&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else </em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Il manque un truc&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n    }\n    <em>?>\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Additionner deux heures, résultat en seconde</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Additionner deux heures, résultat en seconde </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Additionner deux heures, résultat en seconde </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>déclaration : h, m, s, ms, hs, stot : int</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir heure”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (h)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir minute”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (m)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir seconde”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (s)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>ms &lt;- m * 60</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>hs &lt;- h * 60 * 60</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>s_total &lt;- s + ms + hs</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (s_total)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin additionner_heure</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>int </em>h, m, s, ms, hs, s_total;\n\n    printf(\"Saisir heure \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;h);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir minute \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;m);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir seconde \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;s);\n\n    ms = m * 60;\n    hs = h * 60 * 60;\n    s_total = s + ms + hs;\n\n    printf(\"Seconde total = %d\", s_total);\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"CalculerTemps.php\" <em>method</em>=\"post\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"heure\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Heure\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"minute\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Minute\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"seconde\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Seconde\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'heure\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'minute\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'seconde\'])) {\n            $heure = $_POST[\'heure\'];\n            $min = $_POST[\'minute\'];\n            $sec = $_POST[\'seconde\'];\n\n            $heure *= 3600;\n            $min *= 60;\n            $totla = $heure + $min + $sec;\n\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Seconde : $totla&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else</em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Il manque un truc&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n    }\n    <em>?>\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'COURS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '243-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-11-02 17:14:52', '2021-11-02 16:14:52', '', 243, 'http://localhost/projetgroupe/?p=722', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` (`ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(721, 1, '2021-11-02 17:14:25', '2021-11-02 16:14:25', '<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":377,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/shema-groupe-cours/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":27} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\" style=\"grid-template-columns:27% auto\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/shema-groupe-cours-2.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-377 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"textColor\":\"vivid-red\",\"fontSize\":\"huge\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-vivid-red-color has-text-color has-huge-font-size\">Les notions générales :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>1-</strong> Phase d\'élaboration d\'un programme :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Un programme avant son introduction en production (opérationnelle) se passe en <strong>4 phases </strong>: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Phase d\'<strong>analyse</strong></li><li>Phase de <strong>spécialisation</strong></li><li>Phase de <strong>traduction</strong></li><li>Phase d\'<strong>exécution</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br><strong>2-</strong> Phase d’analyse :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A partir du cahier des charges ( besoin du client) du problème posé en informatique, le concepteur de la solutions doit élaborer un <strong>modèle conceptuel d’analyse</strong> (MCA) qui décrit la solution sous la forme d’une suite d’étapes et d’actions.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Deux méthodes sont formaliser dans la création du MCA&nbsp;: </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":387,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/capture-6/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-8.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-387 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>2.1. </strong>La méthode <strong>ascendante&nbsp;</strong>: le concepteur compose la solution informatique du problème à partir d’une <strong>boîte à outils&nbsp; algorithme</strong> élémentaire (connu et maîtrisé). Il obtient&nbsp;un arbres sur divisé en niveaux de difficulté ascendante&nbsp;chaque étape est composée d’action simples.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":390,\"mediaLink\":\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/cours-2/capture-7/\",\"mediaType\":\"image\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-9.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-390 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Contenu…\"} -->\n<p><strong>2.2.</strong> &nbsp;La méthode <strong>descente&nbsp;</strong>: le concepteur&nbsp;<strong>subdivise </strong>le problème posé en plusieurs sous problèmes. Si ces derniers&nbsp;n’ont pas de <strong>solutions simples ou connues</strong>, ils seront de nouveau subdivisés. on obtient alors un arbres subdiviser au niveau de difficulté descendant.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exemple 1&nbsp;:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Elaborer un MCA qui permet la préparation d’une omelette :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":385,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-6.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-385\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exemple 2&nbsp;: Elaborer un MCA qui calcul la moyenne de trois notes&nbsp;:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":386,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-7.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-386\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Exercice :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Elaborer un MCA qui permet de calculer la surface et le périmètre d’un rectangle:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":381,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-381\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Elaborer un MCA qui permet de&nbsp; saisir un temps exprimer en heure, min, sec et afficher son équivalent en seconde.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":382,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-4.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-382\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br><br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>MCA algorithme</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n\n<p class=\"para-cours\">\nSaisir: <br>\nn1, n2, n3 <br> <br>\nOpération: <br>\nSomme = n1 + n2 + n3 <br>\nMoyenne = Somme / 3  <br><br>\nAfficher: <br>\nMoyenne\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Langage : C</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>float </em>n;\n    <em>float </em>note;\n    <em>float </em>somme = 0, moy;\n    printf(\"Combien de note voulez-vous saisir ?\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;n);\n\n    <em>for </em>(<em>int </em>i = 0; i &lt; n; i++){\n        printf(\"Saisir note \\n>>\");\n        scanf(\"%f\", &amp;note);\n        somme += note;\n    }\n\n    moy = somme / n;\n\n    printf(\"Moyenne note = %.2f\", moy);\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"level\":1} -->\n<h1 class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>Langage : PHP</strong></h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<h3>Calcul d\'une moyenne de 3 notes</h3>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form action=\"moyenne.php\" method=\"post\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n1\" placeholder=\"Note 1\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n2\" placeholder=\"Note 2\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"number\" name=\"n3\" placeholder=\"Note 3\"&gt;\n    &lt;input type=\"submit\" name=\"btn\" value=\"OK\"&gt;\n&lt;/form&gt;</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted -->\n\n<!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;?php\n$_note1 = $_POST[\'n1\'];\n$_note2 = $_POST[\'n2\'];\n$_note3 = $_POST[\'n3\'];\n$somme = $_note1 + $_note2 + $_note3;\n$moy = round($somme / 3, 2);\necho \"&lt;p&gt;Moyenne : $moy&lt;/p&gt;\";\n?&gt;</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\">Calcul surface &amp; périmètre</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\"> Calcul surface &amp; périmètre </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"has-text-align-left\"> Calcul surface &amp; périmètre </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>declaration : L, l, peri, surface = réel</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"saisir longueur\")</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (L)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"saisir largeur\")</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (l)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>peri &lt;- 2 * L + 2 * l</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>surface &lt;- L * l</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"surface: \", surface)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (\"perimètre: \", péri)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin calcul_surface_perimetre</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n</strong>\n<strong><em>int </em>main() {\n    <em>float </em>L, l, peri, surface;\n\n    printf(\"Saisir la longueur \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;L);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir la largeur \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;l);\n\n    peri = 2 * L + 2 * l;\n    surface = L * l;\n\n    printf(\"Perim%ctre = %f\\n\", 130, peri);\n    printf(\"Surface = %f\", surface);\n    <em>return </em>0;\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"rectangle.php\" <em>method</em>=\"POST\">\n\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"text\" <em>name</em>=\"longueur\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Longueur\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"text\" <em>name</em>=\"Largeur\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Largeur\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"reset\" <em>value</em>=\"Annuler\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'longueur\']) &amp;&amp; !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'Largeur\'])) {\n            $longueur = $_POST[\'longueur\'];\n            $largeur = $_POST[\'Largeur\'];\n\n            $sur = $longueur * $largeur;\n            $peri = 2 * ($longueur * $largeur);\n\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>surface : $sur\";\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;br>\";\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Périmètre : $peri&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else</em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>il manque quelque chose&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n\n    }\n\n\n    <em>?>\n\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Calculer l\'aire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Calculer l\'aire  </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Calculer l\'aire  </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Déclaration : RT, RL, TL, R = réel</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir RT”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (RT)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir RL”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (RL)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir TL”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (TL)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir R”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (R)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A1 &lt;- TL * RT * 2</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A2 &lt;- (R - RL) * TL</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>A &lt;- A1 - A2</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher(A)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin Aire</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>float </em>RT, RL, TL, R;\n\n    printf(\"Saisir RT\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;RT);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir RL\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;RL);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir TL\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;TL);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir R\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%f\", &amp;R);\n\n    <em>float </em>A1 = TL * RT * 2;\n    <em>float </em>A2 = (R - RL) * TL;\n    <em>float </em>A = A1 - A2;\n\n    printf(\"Aire: %.2f\", A);\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"Aire.php\" <em>method</em>=\"post\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"RT\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"RT\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"RL\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"RL\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"TL\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"TL\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"Rayon\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Rayon\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'RT\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'RL\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'TL\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'Rayon\'])) {\n\n            $RT = $_POST[\'RT\'];\n            $RL = $_POST[\'RL\'];\n            $TL = $_POST[\'TL\'];\n            $Rayon = $_POST[\'Rayon\'];\n\n            $A1 = $TL * $RT * 2;\n            $A2 = ($Rayon - $RL) * $TL;\n            $Aire = $A1 + $A2;\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Aire : $Aire&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else </em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Renseigner tous les champs&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n    }\n    <em>?>\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Salaire</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Salaire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Salaire </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>déclaration</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>heure, jour: entier</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>benef, P, R : entier</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir heure”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (heure)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir jour”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (jour)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir benef”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (benef)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“Pourcentage”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (P)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“R”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (R)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>SB &lt;- R * jour * heure</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Prime &lt;- P * benef / 100</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Salaire &lt;- SB + Prime</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher(Salaire)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin Calcul_Salaire</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>int </em>heure, jour, benef, P, R, SB, Prime, Salaire;\n\n    printf(\"Heure\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;heure);\n\n    printf(\"Jour\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;jour);\n\n    printf(\"benef\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;benef);\n\n    printf(\"pourcentage\\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;P);\n\n    printf(\"r%cmun%cration\\n>>\", 130, 130);\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;R);\n\n    SB = R * jour * heure;\n    Prime = P * benef / 100;\n    Salaire = SB + Prime;\n\n    printf(\"Salaire : %d\", Salaire);\n\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"salaire.php\" <em>method</em>=\"post\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"heure\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Heure\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"jour\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Jour\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"benef\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Benef\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"pourcentage\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Pourcentage\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"remu\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Rémunération\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'heure\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'jour\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'benef\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'pourcentage\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'remu\'])) {\n\n            $heure = $_POST[\'heure\'];\n            $jour = $_POST[\'jour\'];\n            $benef = $_POST[\'benef\'];\n            $pour = $_POST[\'pourcentage\'];\n            $remu = $_POST[\'remu\'];\n\n\n            $SB = $remu * $jour * $heure;\n            $Prime = $pour * $benef / 100;\n            $salaire = $SB + $Prime;\n\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Salaire : $salaire&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else </em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Il manque un truc&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n    }\n    <em>?>\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Additionner deux heure résultat en seconde</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Additionner deux heure résultat en seconde </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3> Additionner deux heure résultat en seconde </h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>déclaration : h, m, s, ms, hs, stot : int</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>début :</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir heure”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (h)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir minute”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (m)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (“saisir seconde”)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>saisir (s)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>ms &lt;- m * 60</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>hs &lt;- h * 60 * 60</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>s_total &lt;- s + ms + hs</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>afficher (s_total)</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>fin additionner_heure</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>#include &lt;stdio.h>\n\n<em>int </em>main(){\n    <em>int </em>h, m, s, ms, hs, s_total;\n\n    printf(\"Saisir heure \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;h);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir minute \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;m);\n\n    printf(\"Saisir seconde \\n>>\");\n    scanf(\"%d\", &amp;s);\n\n    ms = m * 60;\n    hs = h * 60 * 60;\n    s_total = s + ms + hs;\n\n    printf(\"Seconde total = %d\", s_total);\n}</strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:preformatted -->\n<pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\"><strong>&lt;form <em>action</em>=\"CalculerTemps.php\" <em>method</em>=\"post\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"heure\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Heure\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"minute\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Minute\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"number\" <em>name</em>=\"seconde\" <em>placeholder</em>=\"Seconde\">\n    &lt;input <em>type</em>=\"submit\" <em>name</em>=\"btn\" <em>value</em>=\"OK\">\n    <em>&lt;?php\n    if </em>(<em>isset</em>($_POST[\'btn\'])) {\n        <em>if </em>(!<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'heure\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'minute\']) || !<em>empty</em>($_POST[\'seconde\'])) {\n            $heure = $_POST[\'heure\'];\n            $min = $_POST[\'minute\'];\n            $sec = $_POST[\'seconde\'];\n\n            $heure *= 3600;\n            $min *= 60;\n            $totla = $heure + $min + $sec;\n\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Seconde : $totla&lt;/p>\";\n        } <em>else</em>{\n            <em>echo </em>\"&lt;p>Il manque un truc&lt;/p>\";\n        }\n    }\n    <em>?>\n</em>&lt;/form></strong></pre>\n<!-- /wp:preformatted --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'COURS', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '243-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-11-02 17:14:25', '2021-11-02 16:14:25', '', 243, 'http://localhost/projetgroupe/?p=721', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(724, 3, '2021-11-02 20:10:04', '2021-11-02 19:10:04', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\">Le CFA&nbsp;INSTA&nbsp;a été&nbsp;crée&nbsp;en 2009&nbsp;par&nbsp;Ryad&nbsp;Lebib&nbsp;et Hubert&nbsp;Trapet.&nbsp;L’établissement accueille chaque année plus de 600 élèves de&nbsp;tout&nbsp;âge&nbsp;avec un taux de réussite à&nbsp;80%.&nbsp;Le CFA propose des formations adaptées et&nbsp;diplômes&nbsp;reconnues par l’État&nbsp;(titres&nbsp;RNCP&nbsp;et diplômes d’État), en informatique&nbsp;(développement, logiciel et réseaux), en ressources humaines et en comptabilité.&nbsp;Les formations peuvent être faites en alternance&nbsp;(contrat d’apprentissage ou de professionnalisation).&nbsp;L’institut est en partenaire avec plein de TPE et PME et un partenariat depuis 2012 avec Sorbonne Université pour des passerelles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"right\",\"id\":542,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright size-full\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Capture-10.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-542\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":215,\"width\":232,\"height\":151,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/projetgroupe/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Logo-CFAINSTA-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-215\" width=\"232\" height=\"151\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>12 rue de Cléry <br>75002 Paris</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>01 43 36 75 56<br>informatique@cfa-insta.fr</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->', 'L\'ÉCOLE', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '36-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-11-02 20:10:04', '2021-11-02 19:10:04', '', 36, 'http://localhost/projetgroupe/?p=724', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
